a into perspective. In the vein of cinephilia, this study brings together canonical titles (ALS TWEE DRUPPELS WATER; SOLDAAT VAN ORANJE) and little gems (MONSIEUR HAWARDEN; KRACHT). It juxtaposes among others GLUCKAUF and DE VLIEGENDE HOLLANDER (on father figures); FLANAGAN and SPOORLOOS (on rabbles and heroes); DE AANSLAG and LEEDVERMAAK (on historical traumas); ANTONIA and BLUEBIRD (on aphanisis).  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Apr 2022) 0aMotion picturesxHistoryy20th centuryzNetherlands. 0aMotion picturesxPsychological aspects. 0aPsychoanalysis and motion pictureszNetherlands. 4aDutch and The Netherlands. 4aFilm Studies. 4aFilm, Media, and Communication. 4aFilms, cinema. 4aIndividual film directors, film-makers. 4aNetherlands. 4aPsychoanalytical and Freudian psychology. 4aPsychology. 4aTransnational and Global Studies. 7aART / History / Modern (late 19th Century to 1945).2bisacsh  aDutch cinema - psychoanalysis (Freud, Lacan, Zizek) - cinephilia.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertAmsterdam University Press Complete eBook-Package 2021z978311074322708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus PP Package 2021 Part 2z978311074335708iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts 2021z9783110753790oZDB-23-DPK08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Arts, Architecture and Design 2021 Englishz978311075403208iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021 Englishz978311075400108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2021z9783110753776oZDB-23-DGG40uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978904855172940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9789048551729423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9789048551729/original  a978-3-11-074322-7  Amsterdam University Press Comple